Prerequisites
-------------
- JAVA_HOME environment variable must be set
- AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID and AWS_SECRET_KEY environment variables must be set
- javac/java/etc. must be in PATH
- env.sh must be sourced (from project root directory)


Command Line Interface
----------------------
- Make sure the project is built before trying to execute the CLI
- Usage examples:
	* Print the command usage
	./cli.sh -help
	* List the VM definitions
	./cli.sh -listVMDefs
